        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "import pandas as pd"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Importing the Data set"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "OEsC8wKhQV9s"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "dataset = pd.read_csv('/content/studentscores (1) - studentscores (1).csv')\n",
        "x = dataset.iloc[:,:-1].values\n",
        "y = dataset.iloc[:,-1].values"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "eIeTEh1DQUqL"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "splitting the dataset into"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Vdp_HPNgRC3T"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n",
        "x_train, x_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(x,y, test_size=1/3, random_state=0)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "BdnQztK8Rsju"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [

      }

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
